<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 19, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lqt1665702557960.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lqt1665702557960.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lqt1665702557960.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lqt1665702557960\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Internal Data Format\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lqt1665702557960__internal_data_format_55868\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The internal format is a standard format based on the data type of the data concerned, usually combined with the packing code definition. No additional external formatting (such as a display format) is applied. Uniface handles all data in components in the internal format.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lqt1665702557960__p_d16598e1_d16599e1_d16600e1\">The internal formats for handling Date, Time, Datetime, and Boolean data types are shown in the table:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Internal Formats for Handling Date, Time, Datetime, and Boolean Data Types</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__1\">\nType\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__2\">\nInternal\nFormat\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__3\">\nExample\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__1\">\nDate\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__2\">\nccyymmdd\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__3\">\n19940325\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__1\">\nTime\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__2\">\nhhnnsstt\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__3\">\n23595900\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__1\">\nDatetime\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__2\">\nccyymmddhhnnsstt\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__3\">\n1994032523595900\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__1\">\nBoolean\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__2\">\nF or\nT\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lqt1665702557960__table_d1778e1_d1779e1_d1780e1__entry__3\">\nF\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\">For example, consider the field MYDATE with data type D, packing code D2, and display\n            format DIS(DD-MM-YY). The date on the screen appears in the form 09-03-92. However,\n            after the statement, the variable $1 contains 19920903, a date in the format\n                <var class=\"keyword varname\">ccyymmdd</var> (the internal format for data type D) and not DD-MM-YY.\n            :</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"lqt1665702557960__pre_c5k_4dx_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$1 = MYDATE</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Uniface converts to external format—that is, the format associated with the packing code\n            and display format—when the data is displayed or when an implicit type conversion\n            occurs. Implicit type conversion can occur when you use, for example, relational\n            operators between nonmatching types.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529685\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529685\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Internal Data Format Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 19, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Internal Data Format The internal format is a standard format based on the data type of the data concerned, usually combined with the packing code definition. No additional external formatting (such as a display format) is applied. Uniface handles all data in components in the internal format. The internal formats for handling Date, Time, Datetime, and Boolean data types are shown in the table: Table 1. Internal Formats for Handling Date, Time, Datetime, and Boolean Data Types Type Internal Format Example Date ccyymmdd 19940325 Time hhnnsstt 23595900 Datetime ccyymmddhhnnsstt 1994032523595900 Boolean F or T F For example, consider the field MYDATE with data type D, packing code D2, and display format DIS(DD-MM-YY). The date on the screen appears in the form 09-03-92. However, after the statement, the variable $1 contains 19920903, a date in the format ccyymmdd (the internal format for data type D) and not DD-MM-YY. : $1 = MYDATE Copy Uniface converts to external format—that is, the format associated with the packing code and display format—when the data is displayed or when an implicit type conversion occurs. Implicit type conversion can occur when you use, for example, relational operators between nonmatching types. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}